member.name: T:Quickstarts.ReferenceServer.ReferenceServer
member.summary: Implements the Quickstart Reference Server.
member.remarks:
Each server instance must have one instance of a StandardServer object which is responsible for reading the configuration file, creating the endpoints and dispatching incoming requests to the appropriate handler.
This sub-class specifies non-configurable metadata such as Product Name and initializes the EmptyNodeManager which provides access to the data exposed by the Server.
